results.name: aai-vehicles-miner
results.title: AAI Vehicles: Miner
results.summary: A set of mining and excavation vehicles that can quickly mine solid resources such as coal, stone, ores, etc. They also harvest any trees in their path (and can consume the wood as fuel).
